metadata.name: MixTape Headz Society #2
metadata.description: The MixTape Headz Society is unique collection of 10,000 NFTs celebrating the style, retro vibes, and nostalgia of old school music collections. Aside from the unique art work, each MixTape Headz NFT gives exclusive access and discounts to variety of future events including concerts, festivals, AMAs with musicians and other icons as well as discounts on exclusive merchandise.
